#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.kdialog.metainfo.xml:9
msgid ""
"KDialog allows you to display dialog boxes from shell scripts. The syntax is "
"very much inspired from the \"dialog\" command (which shows text mode "
"dialogs)."
msgstr ""
"«KDialog»ek oskoleko gidoietatik elkarrizketa-koadroak azaltzen uzten dizu. "
"Sintaxia \"dialog\" komandoan (testu-moduko elkarrizketa-koadroak erakusten "
"dituena) oso inspiratua dago."
